			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Something that many people sometimes forget to include into their print stylesheets (me included) is they forget to reset the width of the page to 100%, instead of (say) 950px.</p>
<p>Another thing, is people don&#8217;t like reading Navbars, advertisements, and sometimes even comments. You can get rid of these elements in your stylesheet by using the display:none; CSS statement.</p>
<p>Still, this article helped. Thanks Rob!</p>
